import react from "react";
import {BrowserRouter as Router , Routes ,Route,Link} from 'react-router-dom'

import Login from '../Patient/login'
import LoginAdmin from '../Admin/loginAdmin' 
 
export default function Home(){

    return(
        <>
        
    <Router>

    <button className='button'><Link to='/components/Admin/loginAdmin' >

         Admin </Link> </button>

    <button className='button'>  <Link to='/components/Patien/login' exact> 
   Patient </Link> </button>
  
   <Routes>

<Route path='/' exact element={<Home />}/>

<Route path='/components/Admin/loginAdmin'element={<LoginAdmin />}/>


<Route path='AdminHome' element={<adminHome/>}/>

<Route path='components/Patien/login' element ={<Login />}/>

</Routes>


   </Router>
        </>
    )
}
